latestIgtvVideos.title: 'Southern Ode'
latestIgtvVideos.caption: Presenting 'Southern Ode' with chef @hseanbrock. Growing up on a two-acre farm with a storybook Appalachian grandmother, Sean quickly learned the rhythms of the garden. Chores were in the field and the basement was piled high with preserves. In his dish for Freshly, those same traditions of foraging, planting, and preserving live on in a signature touch of sassafras‚Äîa native plant that Sean grew up digging in the mountains. Made from the dried and ground leaves of the sassafras tree, it adds a piquant touch‚Äîsomewhere between earthy citrus and anise‚Äîto a trio of roasted late-summer mushrooms.
